Required Mods
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/17802]Climates Of Tamriel[/url] by [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/1402285]jjc71[/url] (Both versions need this mod)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27043]Enhanced Lights and FX[/url] by [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/1627949]anamorfus[/url] (Both versions need this mod) INSTALL ONLY CORE/MAIN
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/41076]Realistic Water Two[/url] by [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/2463371]isoku[/url] (Full version need this mod)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/48938]Watercolor for ENB and Realistic Water Two[/url] by [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/6375196]paganmetalfan[/url] (Full version need this mod)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/60603]Unofficial ELFX SMIM Performance Patch [/url]by [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/5130874]skysan4298[/url] (Highly recommended mod)
